Title: Undiscovered Treasures
DateModified: '2018-02-06'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/undiscovered-treasures
SetInCountry: Argentina
Category: The last thing I expected
AuthorName: Andrew Bugg
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: Exploring the varying Landscapes of Argentina from the Pampas to Patagonia to
  Tierra del Fuego kayaking biking hiking exploring local cultures and cuisines and
  meeting the locals and getting a close-up encounter with the local wildlife. Having
  local guides show me the countries Treasures like Iguazu Falls and favorite local
  places to hang out.
